Welcome to Texy!
================

This is a sample document written in **Texy markup**.

Basic Formatting
----------------

You can make text **bold** or //italic//.

You can also combine them: **//bold and italic//** text.

Lists
-----

Unordered list:
- First item
- Second item
- Third item
  - Nested item
  - Another nested item

Ordered list:
1. First step
2. Second step
3. Third step

Links
-----

Visit "JBake website":https://jbake.org for more information.

Or use alternative syntax: [JBake|https://jbake.org]

Images
------

You can embed images like this:

[* /images/logo.png *]

Or with alignment:

[* /images/logo.png <*] (left aligned)
[* /images/logo.png >*] (right aligned)

Code Blocks
-----------

Inline code: `System.out.println("Hello");`

Code block:
/--code java
public class HelloWorld {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Hello, Texy!");
    }
}
\--

