Quotes
------

> This is a blockquote.
> It can span multiple lines.
>
> And multiple paragraphs.

Horizontal Rule
---------------

----

Footnotes
---------

This text has a footnote.[*note]

.[*note]: This is the footnote text.

Special Characters
------------------

Texy automatically converts:
- (c) to ©
- (r) to ®
- (tm) to ™
- -- to –
- --- to —
- ... to …

Math and Special Symbols
-------------------------

Texy supports various symbols:
- Arrows: -> <- <=>
- Math: <= >= != +-

Conclusion
----------

Texy is a powerful markup language with many features. For complete documentation, visit "Texy.info":https://texy.info.

